Market Analysis and Size

The over-the-counter (OTC) electromagnetic pulse therapy market is expected to witness significant growth during the forecast period. Acute spinal cord injuries and fractures with delayed healing and non-healing are caused by road accidents and trauma, and these injuries require appropriate surgical intervention. Thus, the over-the-counter electromagnetic pulse therapy market trend is increasing each decade. Rapid advances in medical devices worldwide, changing approaches to therapeutic techniques, and demand for electromagnetic therapy equipment for bone growth are key factors expected to drive the global OTC electromagnetic pulse therapy market growth.

